<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title></title>


  <style type="text/css">
    * {
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    body {
      background: #fff;
      direction: rtl;
      width: 595px;
      height: 842px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 3rem;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      position: relative;
    }

    .header {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .header img {
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
    }

    .header p {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      margin-right: 1rem;
    }

    .spacer {
      flex: 1 1 auto;
    }

    .address-container {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      text-align: start;
    }

    .address-container p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .content-header {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      display: flex;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .content-header h1 {
      flex-basis: 60%;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .content-header table th,
    .content-header table td {
      padding: 4px;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .cutomer-info {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .cutomer-info table {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 0.1rem;
    }

    .cutomer-info table td {
      padding: 0.8rem;
    }

    .product-info {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .product-info table {
      width: 100%;
      border: 2px solid #000;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    .product-info table th,
    .product-info table td {
      padding: 0.6rem;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .product-info table th {
      border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .product-info table td {
      border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
    }


    .price-sum-container {
      display: flex;
    }

    .price-sum {
      display: inline-block;
      border-left: 2px solid #000;
      border-right: 2px solid #000;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
      padding: 0.1rem;
    }

    .price-sum table td {
      padding: 0.6rem;
    }

    .notes-container {
      border: 1px solid #000;
      margin-top: 3.4rem;
      height: 100px;
      padding: .3rem;
    }


    .footer {
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }




    .signiture {
      margin-top: 3em;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .signiture div {
      width: 150px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
      height: 1px;
      align-self: flex-end;
      margin-right: .3rem;
    }
  </style>




</head>

<body>

  <div class="container">



    <div class="header">
      <img src="http://localhost:3000/logo.png" />
      <p>سمارت فون باقة - סמארטפון באקה</p>
    </div>


    <div class="address-container">
      <p>באקה אלגרביה - כביש ראשי</p>
      <p>טל : 052-2784070</p>
    </div>




    <div class="content-header">
      <h1>חשבונית מס\קבלה: {{id}}</h1>

      <div class="spacer"></div>

      <table>
        <tr>
          <td>עוסק מורשה</td>
          <td>30123123</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>תאריך</td>
          <td>{{todayDate}}</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>


    <p>לכבוד</p>




    <div class="cutomer-info">
      <table>
        <tr>
          <td>שם: {{fullName}}</td>
          <td>ת"ז: {{idNumber}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>כתובת: {{address}}</td>
          <td>טל: {{phoneNumber}}</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>




    <div class="product-info">

      <table>
        <thead>
          <th>אמצעי תשלום</th>
          <th>שם פריט</th>
          <th>סכום</th>
        </thead>


        {{#each products as |pr|}}
        <tr>
          <td>{{changePayment pr.payment}}</td>
          <td>{{pr.name}}</td>
          <td>{{numberWithCommas pr.price}}</td>
        </tr>
        {{/each}}
      </table>
    </div>



    <div class="price-sum-container">
      <div class="spacer"></div>

      <div class="price-sum">

        <table>

          <tr>
            <td>
              סה"כ ש"ח ללא מע"ם
            </td>
            <td>{{maam price 83}}</td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td>
              מע"מ 17.00%
            </td>
            <td>{{maam price 17}}</td>
          </tr>



          <tr>
            <td>
              סה"כ כולל מע"מ
            </td>
            <td>
              {{numberWithCommas price}}
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>

      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="notes-container">
      <p>הערות:</p>
      <p>{{notes}}</p>
    </div>



    <div class="footer">
      <p>תודה שקניתם אצלינו</p>
    </div>


    <div class="signiture">
      <p>חתימה:</p>
      <div></div>
    </div>


  </div>

</body>

</html>
